    Snake Army V2 (Final Version for Daddy TG ğŸ˜ğŸ):
    - Background stays on (dimmed)
    - Snakes move forward from start to end
    - Snakes have random gaps between them (3 to 10 LEDs)
    - Snakes have full brightness
